title: Huevos Trendcheros 1/29: John Chaney, Harsh Writing Advice, The Little Things, Justice League, Wandavision, Silhouette Challenge, Cicely Tyson
itunes:title: Huevos Trendcheros 1/29: John Chaney, Harsh Writing Advice, The Little Things, Justice League, Wandavision, Silhouette Challenge, Cicely Tyson
description:
On this edition of Huevos Trendcheros Jack and Miles discuss the passing of Temple Basketball coach John Chaney, people are giving "harsh" writing advice on twitter, the new HBOMax thriller arrives to mixed reviews, the Snyder cut of 'Justice League' comes with a meal kit and a very Snyder-y poster, the latest Wandavision episode gives more details about the origins and realities of the show, the Silhouette Challenge is popping on TikTok, and Hollywood icon Cicely Tyson has passed.
